item.title: Apollyon: Samurai Story Mission 06 - For Honor Story Mode
item.description: This is a video of the Samurai story missions in the For Honor story mode. For Honor is made by Ubisoft for the PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and PC. The game focuses on three factions of warriors locked in a never-ending conflict. The Knights, Vikings, and Samurai are in constant struggle for control over their lands in both single player and multiplayer online battles.
